			<wp:comment_content><![CDATA[This is the trivial Shoes program from Green Shoes manual

require 'green_shoes'
Shoes.app{button(&quot;Click me!&quot;){alert(&quot;Good job.&quot;)}}

I opened task manager to look at its memory usage:
Each time i click the &quot;click me&quot; button and then 'Ok' (bringing back the program at its initial state) 152 k of memory are wasted, and this keep happening each time i press &quot;Click me&quot;.
Is this a known leaking memory problem?]]></wp:comment_content>
